</div></div></section><section class="sm xbox font-sm" id="db_ds_supplementary-material2_reqid_"><div class="caption p"><span>TABLE S2 Description and classification of variants observed to change classifications over time or between laboratories depicted in Figure 4. Separate tabs are present for different types of variant classifications changes: (a) changes from uncertain to pathogenic or benign, (b) changes from pathogenic to uncertain or benign, (c) changes from benign to pathogenic, (d) changes without clear trend</span></div>
<div class="media p"><div class="caption">
<a href="/articles/instance/8162059/bin/NIHMS1693265-supplement-TABLE_S2_Description_and_classification_of_variants_observed_to_change_classifications_over_time_or_between_laboratories_depicted_in_Figure_4__Separate_tabs_are_present_for_different_types_of_variant_classifications_ch.docx" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" class="usa-link">NIHMS1693265-supplement-TABLE_S2_Description_and_classification_of_variants_observed_to_change_classifications_over_time_or_between_laboratories_depicted_in_Figure_4__Separate_tabs_are_present_for_different_types_of_variant_classifications_ch.docx</a><sup> (46.8KB, docx) </sup>
</div></div></section><section class="sm xbox font-sm" id="db_ds_supplementary-material3_reqid_"><div class="caption p"><span>FIGURE S1 A timeline of ophthalmic gene discoveries with associated diseases is displayed along with distinctive events in genetics and genomics history (Choi et al., 2009; Dryja et al., 1990; Goh &amp; Choi, 2012; Mitchell et al., 1988; Nicoletti et al., 1995; OMIM: Online Mendelian Inheritance in Man, n.d.; Timeline: History of Genomics, n.d.</span></div>
